name: Hemisphere Rings to Support North Shore Animal League America
description:
Lovely and bubbly rings. 
Vivi Sun Jewelry will donate 100% of the sale proceeds ($25) of these rings to North Shore Animal League America, world’s largest no-kill animal shelter.

Materials: Plastic Beads, Resin & Brass
Ring Top Size: 1 1/4″ in Diameter
Original Price: $88

After payment clear, we will make a honor donation in your name to North Shore Animal League America. You will receive a Thank You e-card from NSALA.

*All rings are handmade, therefore layout of the beads will be slightly different from photo.
